(2, 'Which channel for communication do student prefer ?', 'Social media is a key channel, particularly when communicating with prospective students. It’s where your students will go to connect with the university on a human level. Email, your website and telephony are also key channels to consider. For helping to support your self-service strategy and driving digital change.', NULL, '1', 1, '2023-09-11 12:49:42', '2023-09-11 12:49:42'),
